trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <see cref="E:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.ChildChanged" /> and <see cref="E:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.ChildChanged" /> events.
trans-unit.target: Fornece dados para os eventos de <see cref="E:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.ChildChanged" /> e de <see cref="E:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.ChildChanged" /> .

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs> class is used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost> classes when the values of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> properties change.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs> classe é usada pelo <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost> e <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost> classes quando os valores da <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> ou <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> alteração de propriedades.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs.PreviousChild%2A> property to get the previously assigned child control or element.
trans-unit.target: Use o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs.PreviousChild%2A> propriedade para obter o controle filho previamente atribuída ou elemento.

trans-unit.source: The value of the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> property before the new value was assigned.
trans-unit.target: O valor da propriedade <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> antes da atribuição do novo valor.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the value of the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> property before the new value was assigned.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o valor da propriedade <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> antes da atribuição do novo valor.

trans-unit.source: The value of the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> property before the new value was assigned.
trans-unit.target: O valor da propriedade <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> antes da atribuição do novo valor.
